### ZodError Class Definition - TypeScript

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs-v3/ERROR_HANDLING.md

Defines the ZodError class structure that extends the native Error class. ZodError instances contain an issues array that stores all validation problems encountered during validation. This is the primary error type thrown by Zod validators.

```typescript
class ZodError extends Error {
  issues: ZodIssue[];
}
```

