### Set Global Zod Error Map

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs-v3/ERROR_HANDLING.md

Demonstrates how to set a global error map using `z.setErrorMap`. This map applies to all Zod validations unless overridden by higher-priority, more specific error maps. The `myErrorMap` variable should be a `z.ZodErrorMap` type.

```ts
const myErrorMap: z.ZodErrorMap = /* ... */;
z.setErrorMap(myErrorMap);
```

