### Define Zod Schema for Form Data

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs-v3/ERROR_HANDLING.md

Defines a Zod object schema named `FormData` for validating form inputs. It includes a required `name` string and a nested `contactInfo` object with a required `email` (validated as an email address) and an optional `phone` string.

```ts
const FormData = z.object({
  name: z.string(),
  contactInfo: z.object({
    email: z.string().email(),
    phone: z.string().optional()
  })
});
```

